From adrian Adrian Nye Subject Re Keyboard mapping and window placement questions If I use Xt all O'Reilly has to say is ' automatically handled by ' If I use Xlib ala XNextEvent I get This all stems from problems with users of the Sun keyboard and the NumLock plus various Alt Meta modifier That's not all it The coverage of modifiers is in Chapter of Volume Four or chap in older Athena editions where there is about pages on how to specify translations to capture various combinations of keys or The Xlib route uses XLookupString and there is a lot of coverage of how that works in Volume One chapter You should read this to understand how all the mappings work before trying to do anything Adrian Nye O'Reilly and Associates